products.title: Adorable Kawaii Bear Ceramic Bowl - Perfect for Fruits, Noodles, and Salads - Cute Korean Kitchen Tableware and Utensils
products.body_html:
Introducing the Kawaii Bear Bowl Plate - a delightful addition to your kitchen that combines functionality with adorable design! Perfect for kids and the young at heart, this cute ceramic bowl is perfect for serving breakfast, salads, fruits, and more, making every meal a joyful experience.

 

Highlights

Experience the charm of our bear bowl and plate, crafted with high-quality ceramics that ensure durability and style.

Featuring a creative bear design, these pieces are not only easy to hold but also anti-scalding, making them safe for everyone.

With a comfortable texture and easy-to-clean surface, these bowls are ideal for everyday use.

Made from matte porcelain, please note that these items are not microwave or oven safe but are dishwasher friendly for effortless cleaning.

Specification

Material: Ceramics

Size: Approximately 6 inches and 8 inches

Notice

- Don't forget to follow our store for exclusive discounts available only to our fans!

- Due to variations in measurement methods, please allow for slight size deviations. Color discrepancies may occur due to different monitor settings. Thank you for your understanding.

- We are committed to providing you with the best product and service. If you encounter any issues, please reach out to us, and we will resolve them promptly. Thank you for your support!

Product Details

Package Contents

1 x Bowl or Plate

Notices

1. We welcome both wholesale and drop shipping orders. You can place orders as needed, and we will strive to ship your products as quickly as possible.

2. Please note that buyers are responsible for any customs taxes that may apply. We are unable to cover customs charges.

3. Ensure that the consignee's information is accurate when placing your order. Russian customers must provide their full name.

Customer Service

1. All products undergo careful inspection and are packed securely before shipping.

2. If you are satisfied with our products and services, please leave positive feedback and a 5-star rating. Your feedback is invaluable to us.

3. If you are not completely satisfied, please contact us before leaving a negative or neutral review. We are dedicated to resolving any issues for you.

products.title: Thomas & Friends Birthday Party Essentials: Disposable Balloon Cups, Plates, and Tablecloth for Kids' Celebrations
products.body_html:
Transform your child's birthday party into a whimsical adventure with our Thomas&Friends Kids Birthday Party Balloon Paper Cups, Plates, and Tablecloth Set!


100% Brand new and high quality, these delightful tableware supplies are designed to bring joy and excitement to any occasion, especially for little Thomas the Tank Engine fans.
Each set includes durable and easy-to-carry paper cups, plates, and a vibrant tablecloth, making clean-up a breeze while keeping the fun going! Perfect for birthday parties, baby showers, and other celebrations.

 
Made from high-quality cowhide paper, our disposable tableware is sturdy and eco-friendly, ensuring a guilt-free party experience.
Colorful designs featuring beloved characters from the Thomas & Friends series will capture the hearts of your little guests and add a touch of magic to your party decor.
Notice:
 
Please allow 1-2mm error due to manual measurement and ensure you do not mind before ordering.
Due to different monitor and camera lights, slight color differences may occur, but rest assured, the appearance is entirely consistent with the pictures provided.

Make your child's special day unforgettable with our charming Thomas&Friends tableware set, designed for fun and convenience!

products.title: Ultimate Circus Theme Birthday Party Supplies - Disposable Cups, Plates, Banners, Clown Balloons & More!
products.body_html:
Bring the magic and excitement of the circus to your child's birthday celebration with our Circus Theme Birthday Party Decorations! This vibrant and fun-filled set includes everything you need to create a memorable event, featuring adorable circus clown designs that are sure to delight guests of all ages.

Our package includes disposable paper cups and plates, a colorful banner, and playful balloons, all designed to complement your carnival-themed festivities. The high-quality cowhide paper ensures durability while remaining eco-friendly, making clean-up a breeze after the party.

Each piece in this set is crafted with attention to detail, showcasing charming animal patterns that capture the essence of a lively circus. Perfect for birthday parties, baby showers, or any festive occasion, these decorations will transform your space into a whimsical wonderland.

Key features:

  • Theme: Circus party
  • Material: Eco-friendly cowhide paper
  • Package includes: Disposable paper cups, plates, banner, and balloons
  • Number of pieces: 6 pcs
  • Origin: Mainland China
  • Customizable options available

Make your celebration unforgettable with our Circus Theme Birthday Party Decorations. Order now and let the festivities begin!
